@node Installing optional backends
@section Installing optional backends

The @samp{transformers} and @samp{nemo} backends need extra Python dependencies.  From
the repository root:

@example
uv sync --project cli --extra transformers
# or
uv sync --project cli --extra nemo
@end example

Or from @samp{cli/}:

@example
uv pip install .[transformers]
uv pip install .[nemo]
@end example

